problems.name: Math Function

problems.description: We practice how to create a function before, now try to create a function to calculate the rectangular area. HINT: side * side = area.
problems.solution:
def area_of_rectangle(side1, side2):
    side1 *= 4
    side2 += 2
    side1 /= 4
    side2 -= 2
    return side1*side2
problems.name: More Functions
